### Lecturer Upload Files Example

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8386
@lecturerToken = Bearer your-lecturer-jwt-token-here
@notebookId = notebook-uuid-here

### OPTION A: Simple Upload (Khuyến nghị - Dễ test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/lecturer/notebooks/{{notebookId}}/files/simple
Authorization: {{lecturerToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

# Chỉ cần upload files, không cần config
# Trong Postman/Thunder Client:
# - Chọn Body > form-data
# - Key: files, Type: File, Value: chọn file PDF/Word

### OPTION B: Advanced Upload (Cho người dùng nâng cao)
POST {{baseUrl}}/lecturer/notebooks/{{notebookId}}/files
Authorization: {{lecturerToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="request"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chunkSize": 3000,
  "chunkOverlap": 250
}

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="Java_Chapter1.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./path/to/Java_Chapter1.pdf

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

