### Get files by notebook (Lecturer)
GET {{baseUrl}}/lecturer/notebooks/{{notebookId}}/files
Authorization: {{lecturerToken}}

### Get accessible notebooks (Lecturer)
GET {{baseUrl}}/lecturer/notebooks/accessible
Authorization: {{lecturerToken}}

### Get all accessible files (Lecturer)
GET {{baseUrl}}/lecturer/notebooks/files?search=java&limit=50
Authorization: {{lecturerToken}}

### Get file detail (Lecturer)
GET {{baseUrl}}/lecturer/notebooks/{{notebookId}}/files/file-uuid-here
Authorization: {{lecturerToken}}

### Delete file (Lecturer)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/lecturer/notebooks/{{notebookId}}/files/file-uuid-here
Authorization: {{lecturerToken}}

### Hướng dẫn test với Postman/Thunder Client

#### Option A: Simple Upload (Dễ nhất)
1. Chọn POST method
2. URL: http://localhost:8386/lecturer/notebooks/{notebookId}/files/simple
3. Headers: Authorization: Bearer your-token
4. Body > form-data:
   - Key: files
   - Type: File  
   - Value: Chọn file PDF hoặc Word
5. Send

#### Option B: Advanced Upload
1. Chọn POST method  
2. URL: http://localhost:8386/lecturer/notebooks/{notebookId}/files
3. Headers: Authorization: Bearer your-token
4. Body > form-data:
   - Key: request, Type: Text, Value: {"chunkSize": 3000, "chunkOverlap": 250}
   - Key: files, Type: File, Value: Chọn file PDF hoặc Word
5. Send

### Giá trị config khuyến nghị:
- File ngắn (< 10 trang): {"chunkSize": 3000, "chunkOverlap": 200}
- File trung bình (10-50 trang): {"chunkSize": 3500, "chunkOverlap": 250}  
- File dài (> 50 trang): {"chunkSize": 4000, "chunkOverlap": 300}